OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"I'm not taking sides." Conservative
OL,7,Fleader, Kemi Badenoch, told GMB, "We
OL,8,Fneed to stop using race as a way of
OL,9,Fdefining laws"
OL,11,FKemi Badenoch has said "whipping
OL,12,Fpeople up" and "making them angry" is
OL,13,Fnot the correct response to the
OL,14,Fstabbing and arrest of teenager Henry
OL,15,FNowak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
