CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe comments by the Conservative party
OL,7,Fleader come after Nigel Farage issued
OL,8,Fa statement about the case on Tuesday,
OL,9,Fsuggesting that we are "living in two-
OL,10,Ftier Britain where the rights and
OL,11,Fprivileges of white people matter less
OL,12,Fthan those of ethnic minorities".
OL,14,F"It is making me angry because that's
OL,15,Fnot how we solve this. That's not how
OL,16,Fwe solve this. We can't solve it by
OL,17,Fwhipping people up. We can't solve it
OL,18,Fby making them angry," Badenoch said
OL,19,Fon Good Morning Britain on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
