PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"Nigel Farage is taking sides. I'm not
OL,7,Ftaking sides. I'm saying enough of
OL,8,Fthis. We need to stop this racialising
OL,9,Fof our society. We are multiracial
OL,10,Fyes, but we need to stop using race as
OL,11,Fa way of defining laws ... Let's treat
OL,12,Feveryone equally."
