OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage showing the
OL,7,Farrest of teenager Mr Nowak, and him
OL,8,Ffalling unconscious as it happens, was
OL,9,Freleased on Monday, after the man
OL,10,Fresponsible for his murder was
OL,11,Fsentenced to at least 21 years in
OL,12,Fprison.
OL,14,FThe video appeared to show the 18-year-
OL,15,Fold, who had received two stab wounds
OL,16,Fon the back his legs and a fatal wound
OL,17,Fto his heart, repeatedly saying "I've
OL,18,Fbeen stabbed" while being handcuffed.
OL,26,@yD@aOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
