PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FIn December Vickrum Digwa, 23, stabbed
OL,7,FMr Nowak five times with a 21cm blade
OL,8,Fthat he said he carried as part of his
OL,9,FSikh faith.
OL,11,FThe footage showed Mr Nowak grunting
OL,12,Fand repeating "I've been stabbed" and
OL,13,F"I can't breathe" while he is made to
OL,14,Fsit up to be handcuffed.
OL,16,FA police officer at the scene can be
OL,17,Fheard asking: "You've been stabbed,
OL,18,Fwhereabouts?" before adding: "Don't
OL,19,Fthink you have, mate."
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@aO]uD@AOUuD@QO]yD@OOUzD@MO]zD@
OL,26,A^OU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
