OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe officer can be heard saying: "He
OL,7,Fsays he's been stabbed, so let's just
OL,8,Fcheck him" and appears to briefly lift
OL,9,Fhis shirt around the belt area before
OL,10,FMr Nowak is left to lie on his side.
OL,12,FA female officer can then be heard
OL,13,Fasking: "Where do you think he's been
OL,14,Fstabbed? In the face?" to which a male
OL,15,Fvoice replies: "He hasn't been
OL,16,Fstabbed."
OL,18,FMr Nowak, who seems unresponsive, is
OL,19,Fthen told he is being arrested for
OL,20,Fassault.
OL,26,@nD@bOUpD@JO]uD@IOUvD@VO]wD@POUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
