OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FDigwa had told police that Mr Nowak
OL,7,Fhad racially abused him before
OL,8,Fpunching him and knocking his turban
OL,9,Foff.
OL,11,FHe said he had stabbed Mr Nowak in
OL,12,Fself-defence after Mr Nowak had
OL,13,Fthreatened him and grabbed him by the
OL,14,Fhair, but said he had not realised at
OL,15,Fthe time he had caused the fatal stab
OL,16,Fwound to his chest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
