PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780413074
OL,3,CBadenoch says 'making people angry'
OL,4,Cwrong response to Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FDuring the trial, the prosecution said
OL,7,FDigwa had "lied" and deceived officers
OL,8,Fwho attended the scene by claiming
OL,9,Fthat he had not stabbed Mr Nowak
OL,10,Fdespite the student's pleas for help.
OL,12,FThe Council of Southampton Gurwaras,
OL,13,Fwhich represents Sikhs in the city,
OL,14,Fstrongly condemned the attack.
OL,16,F"Crimes of this nature must not be
OL,17,Fused to foster division between
OL,18,Fcommunities or to weaken the bonds
OL,19,Fthat hold society together," it said
OL,20,Fin a statement on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
